<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Project Summary</title>
    <style>
        /* CSS styles */
        .container {
            max-width: 90%;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #d0d0e1;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);
        }

        .article-heading {
            width: 40%;
            background-color: #00264d;
            font-size: 26px;
            font-weight: bold;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            color: whitesmoke;
            margin-left: 30%;
            margin-right: 30%;
            padding: 8px;
            text-align: center;
            border: 1px solid black;
            border-radius: 10px;
            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px #333;
        }

        .summary-list {
            list-style-type: disc;
            padding-left: 20px;
            color: #555;
            font-size:16px;
        }

            .summary-list li {
                margin-bottom: 10px;
                line-height: 1.6;
            }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="container">
        <article>
            <h2 class="article-heading">Summary of the Project</h2>
            <ul class="summary-list">
                <li>Define the project scope and objectives.</li>
                <li>Identify key stakeholders and their roles.</li>
                <li>Establish a project timeline with milestones.</li>
                <li>Allocate resources and assign tasks.</li>
                <li>Monitor progress and adjust plans as necessary.</li>
                <li>Ensure quality control and risk management.</li>
                <li>Conduct regular status meetings and updates.</li>
                <li>Deliver the final project and review outcomes.</li>
            </ul>
        </article>
    </div>

</body>
</html>
